! 1.3.3
* Fixed CreateGaugeModal widget syntax errors (extra `}}`,`>>>>`) that caused `> 目标条目 >` display corruption and tag-picker failure.
* Fixed `标签` field: replaced broken `{{||$:/core/ui/EditTemplate/tags}}` transclusion with direct `tag-picker-body` helper.
* Fixed `tagListFilter` to default to `[all[tiddlers]!is[system]sort[title]]` when `targetTiddlerFilter` is blank, so dropdown shows proper tiddler suggestions instead of "找不到标签".
* Rewrote E2E tests to simulate real user flow (button click → template select → tag entry).
! 1.3.2
* Fixed quick-create gauge modal `targetTiddler` field: tag picker now properly accepts custom entries via the add button.
* Fixed `targetTiddler` filter expression that caused "Missing [ in filter expression" error when empty.
* Refactored modal tag picker to use core `tag-picker` macro directly, eliminating nested field wrappers.
* Added Playwright regression test for modal tag picker custom entry behavior.
* Added plugin changelog file for release tracking.
